text:
Bro
The Macho man of Wing D5, gym lover, fitness freak. Aur kya kya visheshtayein batai jaaye aapki. Wing mein bulla sessions mein kya entertainment hota tha yaar. I wish last ke kuch dino mein, main bhi hota wing mein sabke saath. But koi nai, hope ki apne Dual Degree ke aakri saal mein aur time spend karne ka mauka mile apan ko.
Wishing you great achievements in all your future endeavours
author: Aman  Raj

text:
Pandey Sir
Aapke saath kaam karke bahaut maza aaya aur bahaut kuch seekhne ko bhi mila. Tumhara dedication aur professionalism dekh ke motivation milta hai bhai. To all the good times that we have spent together in classes and labs. Wo night out abhi bhi yaad hai presenatation ke ek din pehle
Wishing that you achieve great heights in your career
author: Aman  Raj

text:
Anuj Bhai
Bahaut time spend kiya hai apan ne saath mein MSE ke courses mein. Remembering those nightouts preparing for exams, assignments, projects. Bahaut competitive bande ho bhai tum, your attitude towards life is great. I am glad that we met. And wish that our paths cross again sometime
Wishing you great success in all your future endeavours.
author: Aman  Raj

text:
Yo Tuuuuull
Bhai cricket ka fan ho to koi tumhare jaisa. Bahaut time saath spend kiya hai apan ne aur abhi to ek aur saal hai.  Bahaut yaad aayenge wo din jab humari poori wing saath mein hua karti thi, bahaut maze kiye hai apan ne. Badminton court se lekar gully cricket tak, dinner outings se lekar late night campus tour tak, wing mein bulla sessions se lekar Antaragni night tak. Kaash wo din waapas aa jayein. 
To our friendship and all the great times together. Wishing you all the great success in all your future endeavours. Aise hi muskuraate raho.ðŸ˜‰
author: Aman  Raj

text:
Bhai
Tum hi the jisko maine apna pehla Bhai maana College mein. Ghar se pehli baar door hone par ek bhai se door hua par ek naya bhai mil gaya. Ek saal hi saath mein guzaara apan ne sahi maayna mein par wo din hi to best the. I wish ki in the last 4 years, hume aur samay milta saath mein but life has its own ways . I am getting a bit senti writing this ðŸ˜‚ðŸ˜‚ remembering all the moments we have spent together.
You are the most ambitious and hardworking guy that I have ever met.  Always striving for perfection setting higher goals. Bahaut kuch seekhne ko mila tumse. LOL I am crying writing this. 
Although hum saath mein utna time nai spend kar paaye jitna hume karna chahiye that but I wish and hope our paths cross again sometime.
author: Aman  Raj

text:
Yo Naman
Journey kaafi achi rahi apni in 4 saalon ki. Kaafi maze kiye apan ne from the dinner outings to the late night discussions, from playing badminton on the court to the gully cricket in our wings and ofcourse to PubG, from the great enjoyment in the fests to some serious discussions. Bahaut kuch seekhne ko mila tumse. Aur bhai tera confidence level to alag hi level pe hai, mujhe bhi chahiye bhai aisa confidence. Bahaut assignments mein bhi tumne beda paar lagawa hai. Will miss all the movie nights, the great intellectual discussions, the various talks we attended together towards the common goal, campus hangouts.
I think and hope our paths will cross again. Till then wishing you all the very best for all the upcoming endeavours.
author: Aman  Raj

text:
Bhai,
Bahaut kam hai iss duniya mein tumhare jaise log jo bina kisi expectation ke dusron ki madad karne ke liye humesha taiyar rehte hai. You have helped me a lot bro through these 4 years. Iss duniya ko zaroorat hai tumhare jaise logon ki. Last 4 years college ke saath hi rahe hai apan.
Hope we cross paths again. Wishing you success in all the endeavours in your life.
author: Aman  Raj

text:
Bhai
First Year se Fourth year tak saath raha humara. I wish ye saath choote na but our paths are different and so are our goals. Abhi ke liye to saath choot raha hai but IIMA join karne ke baad bhul na jaana humein. Chaapu bro, the most intelligent person that I know. You have the sharpest mind among all the people that I know of. Aise hi chaapte raho aage bhi.  Anginat baar planning karne ke baad aakhirkar apni Ek wing trip to ho hi gayi. Bahaut maze kiye apan ne saath mein Rajasthan trip par. Hope ki aisa mauka phir mile. Will always remember the times we spent together in the Wing. All the dinner outings and small campus tours, the gully cricket in our wing to the Badminton nights. Wo din to waapas nai aayenge, but we can keep the memories alive.ðŸ˜‡ðŸ˜‡
Wishing you great success in all your future endeavours. Hope hum jald hi mile.
author: Aman  Raj

text:
Bhai
1st year se 4th year tak saath hi mein rahe hai apan. Spent some great times together. Tumse zaada real banda nai dekha maine. Always ready to help and always caring. Kabhi kabhi to lagta hai aapko insaanon se zaada jaanwaron se lagav haiðŸ˜‚. But truly this world needs more people like you. Bilkul orginal without any veil.

Wishing you great success in all your future endeavours. Waise abhi 1 saal aur hai apan saath mein.
